00:33:53,333 --> 00:33:54,866
<c.Japanese>（冬島）失言大臣の次は<c.Japanese>—</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

688
00:33:55,566 --> 00:33:58,500
<c.Japanese>おしゃぶり官房長官が
