689
00:33:59,000 --> 00:34:01,900
<c.Japanese>総理の任命責任を含め<c.Japanese>—</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

690
00:34:02,333 --> 00:34:03,566
<c.Japanese>ご自身のお考えを<c.Japanese>—</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

691
00:34:03,666 --> 00:34:06,866
<c.Japanese>この場で はっきりと
