00:35:35,633 --> 00:35:36,433
<c.Japanese>おしゃぶりだとか<c.Japanese>—</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

722
00:35:36,533 --> 00:35:37,466
<c.Japanese>よだれかけだとか<c.Japanese>—</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

723
00:35:37,566 --> 00:35:38,266
<c.Japanese>ＳＭだとか<c.Japanese>—</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

724
00:35:38,366 --> 00:35:40,400
<c.Japanese>そんなくっだらないこと
どうだっていいじゃないですか</c.Japanese>

725
00:35:40,500 --> 00:35:41,833
<c.Japanese>（ヤジ）</c.Japanese>

726
00:35:42,000 --> 00:35:43,233
<c.Japanese>皆さんは<c.Japanese>—</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

727
00:35:43,866 --> 00:35:46,966
<c.Japanese>僕から見て どう見ても<c.Japanese>—</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

728
00:35:47,500 --> 00:35:48,300
<c.Japanese>大人です</c.Japanese>

729
00:35:48,400 --> 00:35:52,366
<c.Japanese>（ヤジ）</c.Japanese>

730
00:35:54,933 --> 00:35:56,466
<c.Japanese>もっと大人になりましょうよ</c.Japanese>

731
00:35:58,166 --> 00:36:00,633
<c.Japanese>（議員）“くだらない”とは
どういうことなんですか？</c.Japanese>

732
00:36:00,733 --> 00:36:01,866
<c.Japanese>総理 総理</c.Japanese>

733
00:36:02,333 --> 00:36:04,633
<c.Japanese>総理は女の敵ですよ</c.Japanese>

734
00:36:04,733 --> 00:36:09,200
<c.Japanese>（ヤジ）</c.Japanese>

735
00:36:11,433 --> 00:36:12,666
<c.Japanese>僕には…</c.Japanese>

736
00:36:13,166 --> 00:36:14,300
<c.Japanese>僕には そんなつもりありません</c.Japanese>

737
00:36:17,033 --> 00:36:19,566
<c.Japanese>僕は今朝 狩屋さんの奥さんに
会ってきました</c.Japanese>

