00:37:03,366 --> 00:37:04,433
<c.Japanese>狩屋さんは<c.Japanese>—</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

752
00:37:05,733 --> 00:37:07,800
<c.Japanese>僕にとって とても大切な人です</c.Japanese>

753
00:37:09,700 --> 00:37:11,333
<c.Japanese>狩屋官房長官には<c.Japanese>—</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

754
00:37:12,866 --> 00:37:16,766
<c.Japanese>今の政治を
一歩でも前に進めるために<c.Japanese>—</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

755
00:37:18,100 --> 00:37:19,400
<c.Japanese>今の職務を<c.Japanese>—</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

756
00:37:19,566 --> 00:37:21,200
<c.Japanese>まったりしてほしいと思います</c.Japanese>

757
00:37:21,600 --> 00:37:22,933
<c.Japanese>“全う”です</c.Japanese>

758
00:37:24,733 --> 00:37:25,766
<c.Japanese>（翔）それで<c.Japanese>—</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

759
00:37:27,200 --> 00:37:28,833
<c.Japanese>国民の方たちが<c.Japanese>—</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

760
00:37:30,066 --> 00:37:32,766
<c.Japanese>狩屋官房長官では
“ノー”と おっしゃるなら<c.Japanese>—</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

761
00:37:37,500 --> 00:37:38,400
<c.Japanese>僕も<c.Japanese>—</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

