766
00:38:05,100 --> 00:38:06,733
<c.Japanese>ＳＭオヤジ 今どこにいるの？</c.Japanese>

767
00:38:06,833 --> 00:38:07,733
<c.Japanese>どうするつもりだ</c.Japanese>

768
00:38:08,433 --> 00:38:10,000
<c.Japanese>とにかく じかに話聞いてくる</c.Japanese>

769
00:38:10,100 --> 00:38:11,400
<c.Japanese>何を勝手なことを</c.Japanese>

770
00:38:17,100 --> 00:38:18,100
<c.Japanese>（一郎のため息）</c.Japanese>

771
00:38:29,233 --> 00:38:30,766
<c.Japanese>お手間は取らせません</c.Japanese>

772
00:38:32,466 --> 00:38:34,866
<c.Japanese>どこの議員の
路チュー写真かと思えば<c.Japanese>—</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

773
00:38:34,966 --> 00:38:35,833
<c.Japanese>社長<c.Japanese>—</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

774
00:38:36,066 --> 00:38:37,333
<c.Japanese>あなたですね</c.Japanese>

775
00:38:38,833 --> 00:38:40,000
<c.Japanese>相手は つい１か月前<c.Japanese>—</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

776
00:38:40,533 --> 00:38:42,366
<c.Japanese>あなたの推薦で入社した女性社員</c.Japanese>

777
00:38:43,033 --> 00:38:43,500
<c.Japanese>えっ？</c.Japanese>

778
00:38:45,133 --> 00:38:47,433
<c.Japanese>（泰山）
若社長の性根は腐っているようだ</c.Japanese>

779
00:38:49,166 --> 00:38:51,700
<c.Japanese>優秀なシングルマザーを
クビにして<c.Japanese>—</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

780
00:38:52,166 --> 00:38:54,966
<c.Japanese><c.Japanese>仙台</c.Japanese><c.Japanese>(</c.Japanese><c.Japanese>せんだい</c.Japanese><c.Japanese>)</c.Japanese>から連れてきた愛人を
