00:39:17,566 --> 00:39:20,233
<c.Japanese>彼女の働きで取引先は増え<c.Japanese>—</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

788
00:39:20,333 --> 00:39:22,633
<c.Japanese>販売店への指導も行き渡り<c.Japanese>—</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

789
00:39:23,500 --> 00:39:25,966
<c.Japanese>在庫が16パーセントも激減した</c.Japanese>

790
00:39:28,400 --> 00:39:29,466
<c.Japanese>その間<c.Japanese>—</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

791
00:39:30,066 --> 00:39:32,233
<c.Japanese>１人で子供を育てる苦労を<c.Japanese>—</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

792
00:39:32,533 --> 00:39:34,466
<c.Japanese>同僚たちは よく知っている</c.Japanese>

793
00:39:36,200 --> 00:39:38,166
<c.Japanese>出勤前に家事をこなし<c.Japanese>—</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

794
00:39:38,700 --> 00:39:41,233
<c.Japanese>背中にヨーグルトをつけた服で
