795
00:39:42,433 --> 00:39:45,966
<c.Japanese>夜なべして保育園の宿題を作り<c.Japanese>—</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

796
00:39:47,266 --> 00:39:49,233
<c.Japanese>毎日 寝不足なのに<c.Japanese>—</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

797
00:39:50,366 --> 00:39:51,966
<c.Japanese>いつも笑顔で<c.Japanese>—</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

798
00:39:54,000 --> 00:39:56,366
<c.Japanese>本当に よく頑張っていたと</c.Japanese>

799
00:40:05,100 --> 00:40:07,033
<c.Japanese>会社を私物化するな！</c.Japanese>

800
00:40:08,800 --> 00:40:10,400
<c.Japanese>フッ ハハ…</c.Japanese>

801
00:40:11,166 --> 00:40:13,000
<c.Japanese>何を勘違いしてるんだか</c.Japanese>

802
00:40:13,766 --> 00:40:15,733
<c.Japanese>学生のくせに</c.Japanese>

803
00:40:16,066 --> 00:40:16,866
<c.Japanese>ああ？</c.Japanese>

