818
00:41:04,866 --> 00:41:06,700
<c.Japanese>今の社長は私だ！</c.Japanese>

819
00:41:07,766 --> 00:41:08,733
<c.Japanese>私が判断する</c.Japanese>

820
00:41:09,133 --> 00:41:09,966
<c.Japanese>仕事の邪魔だ</c.Japanese>

821
00:41:10,533 --> 00:41:11,366
<c.Japanese>帰りなさい</c.Japanese>

822
00:41:11,466 --> 00:41:13,300
<c.Japanese>（ドアの開く音）</c.Japanese>

823
00:41:13,666 --> 00:41:14,833
<c.Japanese>あの…</c.Japanese>

824
00:41:15,600 --> 00:41:18,633
<c.Japanese>ホントに もういいんです</c.Japanese>

