00:41:21,933 --> 00:41:22,933
<c.Japanese>社長</c.Japanese>

826
00:41:23,966 --> 00:41:25,500
<c.Japanese>お世話になりました</c.Japanese>

827
00:41:27,100 --> 00:41:28,333
<c.Japanese>山里さん</c.Japanese>

828
00:41:33,933 --> 00:41:34,966
<c.Japanese>社長</c.Japanese>

829
00:41:36,000 --> 00:41:37,500
<c.Japanese>お世話になりました</c.Japanese>

830
00:41:39,100 --> 00:41:40,333
<c.Japanese>山里さん</c.Japanese>

831
00:41:45,633 --> 00:41:46,266
<c.Japanese>（桐月）一郎</c.Japanese>

832
00:41:48,266 --> 00:41:50,966
<c.Japanese>お前を社長にしたのは
