<c.Japanese>パパ</c.Japanese>

834
00:41:52,400 --> 00:41:53,966
<c.Japanese>おっ ご無沙汰</c.Japanese>

835
00:41:55,833 --> 00:41:56,633
<c.Japanese>いや</c.Japanese>

836
00:41:57,833 --> 00:41:58,700
<c.Japanese>はじめまして</c.Japanese>

837
00:41:59,666 --> 00:42:02,266
<c.Japanese>君が総理の息子の翔くんか</c.Japanese>

838
00:42:03,166 --> 00:42:04,600
<c.Japanese>教えてくれて ありがとう</c.Japanese>

839
00:42:06,166 --> 00:42:07,766
<c.Japanese>な… 何なんですか</c.Japanese>

840
00:42:09,300 --> 00:42:11,700
<c.Japanese>会社を経営するということは<c.Japanese>—</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

841
00:42:12,600 --> 00:42:15,366
<c.Japanese>トップが いかに
部下を守るかということだ</c.Japanese>

842
00:42:16,866 --> 00:42:17,900
<c.Japanese>切ることではない</c.Japanese>

843
00:42:19,933 --> 00:42:23,200
<c.Japanese>男 狩屋 悔いはありません</c.Japanese>

844
00:42:25,000 --> 00:42:26,566
<c.Japanese>（桐月）トップの判断に<c.Japanese>—</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

845
00:42:26,666 --> 00:42:29,066
<c.Japanese>どんな義があるかということを<c.Japanese>—</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

846
00:42:29,266 --> 00:42:31,366
<c.Japanese>社員たちは常に見ている</c.Japanese>

847
00:42:31,666 --> 00:42:34,133
<c.Japanese>理不尽なトップには
誰もついてこない</c.Japanese>

848
00:42:34,733 --> 00:42:36,133
<c.Japanese>義さえあれば<c.Japanese>—</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

849
00:42:37,033 --> 00:42:39,833
<c.Japanese>一緒に涙をのんでくれることもある</c.Japanese>

850
00:42:39,933 --> 00:42:42,066
<c.Japanese>それが経営というもんだ</c.Japanese>

851
00:42:47,300 --> 00:42:48,500
<c.Japanese>お前を更迭する</c.Japanese>

852
00:42:50,200 --> 00:42:52,066
<c.Japanese>もう一度 一から修業し直してこい</c.Japanese>

853
00:42:52,266 --> 00:42:53,633
<c.Japanese>そんな</c.Japanese>

854
00:42:55,500 --> 00:42:56,700
<c.Japanese>山里さん</c.Japanese>

855
00:42:57,366 --> 00:42:58,800
<c.Japanese>本当に申し訳なかった</c.Japanese>

856
00:42:59,733 --> 00:43:00,533
<c.Japanese>どうか<c.Japanese>—</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

857
00:43:00,633 --> 00:43:03,066
<c.Japanese>今までどおり
うちで働いてください</c.Japanese>

858
00:43:05,266 --> 00:43:06,500
<c.Japanese>ありがとうございます！</c.Japanese>

859
00:43:07,333 --> 00:43:11,200
<c.Japanese>（拍手）</c.Japanese>

860
00:43:11,800 --> 00:43:12,766
<c.Japanese>（桐月）みんな</c.Japanese>

861
00:43:13,633 --> 00:43:17,166
<c.Japanese>また社長として頑張らせてもらうよ</c.Japanese>

862
00:43:17,266 --> 00:43:18,666
<c.Japanese>（社員たち）お願いします 社長</c.Japanese>

863
00:43:18,766 --> 00:43:23,900
<c.Japanese>（拍手）</c.Japanese>

864
00:43:24,000 --> 00:43:27,266
<c.Japanese>まったく 政治も同じだな</c.Japanese>

865
00:43:28,333 --> 00:43:28,800
<c.Japanese>え？</c.Japanese>

866
00:43:29,433 --> 00:43:31,000
<c.Japanese>うん 急がねば</c.Japanese>

867
00:43:31,300 --> 00:43:32,233
<c.Japanese>失敬</c.Japanese>

868
00:43:37,433 --> 00:43:37,933
<c.Japanese>浜…</c.Japanese>

869
00:43:38,500 --> 00:43:39,933
<c.Japanese>（シャッター音）</c.Japanese>

870
00:43:40,133 --> 00:43:41,000
<c.Japanese>（せき払い）</c.Japanese>

871
00:43:41,800 --> 00:43:46,100
<c.Japanese>浜畑議員の
ＳＭクラブの飲食代について<c.Japanese>—</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

872
00:43:46,200 --> 00:43:49,833
<c.Japanese>本人に直接
説明を求めましたところ</c.Japanese>

873
00:43:50,133 --> 00:43:50,866
<c.Japanese>え…</c.Japanese>

874
00:43:51,600 --> 00:43:52,533
<c.Japanese>このとおり<c.Japanese>—</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

875
00:43:54,233 --> 00:43:58,000
<c.Japanese>政治活動費には一切
計上していないことが分かりました</c.Japanese>

876
00:43:58,433 --> 00:44:01,633
<c.Japanese>（泰山）
貝原！　狩屋をクビにするな</c.Japanese>

877
00:44:01,733 --> 00:44:03,866
<c.Japanese>（貝原）
<c.Japanese>その件なら無事に済みましたよ</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

878
00:44:03,966 --> 00:44:04,700
<c.Japanese>え？</c.Japanese>

879
00:44:06,033 --> 00:44:08,566
<c.Japanese>経費の使い方に問題がない以上<c.Japanese>—</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

880
00:44:08,666 --> 00:44:12,500
<c.Japanese>ＳＭクラブ通いは あくまでも
プライベートのことですので<c.Japanese>—</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

881
00:44:13,533 --> 00:44:16,766
<c.Japanese>業務に支障がないかぎり
更迭はないと<c.Japanese>—</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

882
00:44:16,866 --> 00:44:17,800
<c.Japanese>考えております</c.Japanese>

883
00:44:18,000 --> 00:44:19,766
<c.Japanese>（記者）しかし議員は公人です</c.Japanese>

884
00:44:19,866 --> 00:44:21,566
<c.Japanese>議員としての資質が
問われるのでは？</c.Japanese>

885
00:44:21,766 --> 00:44:23,700
<c.Japanese>フランスの元大統領は<c.Japanese>—</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

886
00:44:23,800 --> 00:44:26,466
<c.Japanese>ロンドンサミットに
夫人ではなく<c.Japanese>—</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

887
00:44:26,666 --> 00:44:28,266
<c.Japanese>愛人を同伴しました</c.Japanese>

888
00:44:28,833 --> 00:44:31,200
<c.Japanese>そういうことが
問題にならないのが<c.Japanese>—</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

889
00:44:31,533 --> 00:44:33,533
<c.Japanese>成熟した社会だと<c.Japanese>—</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

890
00:44:34,200 --> 00:44:35,266
<c.Japanese>思っております</c.Japanese>

891
00:44:35,466 --> 00:44:36,666
<c.Japanese>（蔵本のため息）</c.Japanese>

892
00:44:37,100 --> 00:44:39,833
<c.Japanese>いくら何でも言い過ぎだろう</c.Japanese>

893
00:44:39,933 --> 00:44:41,700
<c.Japanese>（記者たちの騒ぐ声）</c.Japanese>

894
00:44:42,200 --> 00:44:44,300
<c.Japanese>（記者）後任については
どう考えているんですか？</c.Japanese>

895
00:44:44,466 --> 00:44:46,133
<c.Japanese>（翔）<c.Japanese>狩屋官房長官には—</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

896
00:44:47,166 --> 00:44:51,166
<c.Japanese>今の政治を
一歩でも前へ進めるために<c.Japanese>—</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

897
00:44:52,466 --> 00:44:53,466
<c.Japanese>今の職務を<c.Japanese>—</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

898
00:44:54,700 --> 00:44:56,233
<c.Japanese>まったりしてほしいと思います</c.Japanese>

899
00:44:57,000 --> 00:44:59,433
<c.Japanese>それで もし国民の人たちが<c.Japanese>—</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

900
00:45:00,100 --> 00:45:02,966
<c.Japanese>狩屋官房長官では
“ノー”と おっしゃるなら<c.Japanese>—</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

901
00:45:05,033 --> 00:45:06,033
<c.Japanese>僕も<c.Japanese>—</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

902
00:45:07,000 --> 00:45:07,900
<c.Japanese>総理 辞めます</c.Japanese>

903
00:45:10,066 --> 00:45:11,600
<c.Japanese>バカ野郎</c.Japanese>

904
00:45:11,833 --> 00:45:14,000
<c.Japanese>お前 俺の内閣をつぶす気か！</c.Japanese>

905
00:45:14,100 --> 00:45:16,633
<c.Japanese>（綾）あら 昔のあなたなら<c.Japanese>—</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

906
00:45:16,933 --> 00:45:18,233
<c.Japanese>翔と同じこと言ったかも</c.Japanese>

907
00:45:19,900 --> 00:45:20,366
<c.Japanese>え？</c.Japanese>

908
00:45:28,633 --> 00:45:29,533
<c.Japanese>イチゴ</c.Japanese>

909
00:45:34,633 --> 00:45:35,333
<c.Japanese>（ドアの開く音）</c.Japanese>

910
00:45:41,366 --> 00:45:42,766
<c.Japanese>あなたのおかげで</c.Japanese><c.Japanese>—</c.Japanese>

911
00:45:46,400 --> 00:45:48,000
<c.Japanese>私 大切なことを学んだ</c.Japanese>

912
00:45:49,966 --> 00:45:50,966
<c.Japanese>ありがとう</c.Japanese>

913
00:45:55,433 --> 00:45:56,466
<c.Japanese>ありがとう</c.Japanese>

914
00:45:57,766 --> 00:45:58,666
<c.Japanese>（狩屋）分かった</c.Japanese>

915
00:46:03,200 --> 00:46:04,233
<c.Japanese>キモいな</c.Japanese>

916
00:46:04,333 --> 00:46:05,666
<c.Japanese>ビジュアル的に かなり</c.Japanese>

917
00:46:07,200 --> 00:46:08,133
<c.Japanese>ありがとう</c.Japanese>

918
00:46:09,433 --> 00:46:11,400
<c.Japanese>（綾）翔
（泰山）ん？</c.Japanese>

919
00:46:12,000 --> 00:46:12,800
<c.Japanese>真衣さんよ</c.Japanese>

920
00:46:14,733 --> 00:46:15,200
<c.Japanese>どうぞ</c.Japanese>

921
00:46:19,600 --> 00:46:20,400
<c.Japanese>（せき払い）</c.Japanese>

922
00:46:24,433 --> 00:46:25,333
<c.Japanese>お礼が言いたくて</c.Japanese>

923
00:46:25,433 --> 00:46:26,633
<c.Japanese>いやあ そんな</c.Japanese>

924
00:46:28,766 --> 00:46:31,733
<c.Japanese>でも どうして若社長が
あんなヤツだって分かったの？</c.Japanese>

925
00:46:32,266 --> 00:46:33,266
<c.Japanese>ああ</c.Japanese>

926
00:46:34,400 --> 00:46:36,666
<c.Japanese>（泰山）<c.Japanese>あんなヤツの本性くらい</c.Japanese>
<c.Japanese>見抜けんで—</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

927
00:46:36,766 --> 00:46:38,366
<c.Japanese>政治家が務まるか</c.Japanese>

928
00:46:41,466 --> 00:46:45,233
<c.Japanese>いやあ 何となく</c.Japanese>
<c.Japanese>オヤジが その…</c.Japanese>

929
00:46:51,066 --> 00:46:52,133
<c.Japanese>（ドアの開く音）</c.Japanese>

930
00:47:01,333 --> 00:47:02,966
<c.Japanese>（真衣）</c.Japanese>
<c.Japanese>翔くんのおかげで</c.Japanese><c.Japanese>—</c.Japanese>

931
00:47:04,766 --> 00:47:06,100
<c.Japanese>私も救われた</c.Japanese>

932
00:47:11,866 --> 00:47:13,066
<c.Japanese>翔くんは</c.Japanese><c.Japanese>—</c.Japanese>

933
00:47:14,633 --> 00:47:17,133
<c.Japanese>私にとって特別な人</c.Japanese>

934
00:47:28,033 --> 00:47:30,033
<c.Japanese>（泰山）</c.Japanese>
<c.Japanese>不測の事態が発生した</c.Japanese>

935
00:47:34,700 --> 00:47:40,700
<c.Japanese>♪〜</c.Japanese>

936
00:48:03,466 --> 00:48:09,466
<c.Japanese>〜♪</c.Japanese>

937
00:48:12,200 --> 00:48:13,600
<c.Japanese>（泰山）地盤 看板</c.Japanese>
<c.Japanese>カバンなら俺のがある</c.Japanese>

938
00:48:13,766 --> 00:48:14,833
<c.Japanese>存分に使うがいい</c.Japanese>

939
00:48:14,933 --> 00:48:15,400
<c.Japanese>いらない！</c.Japanese>

940
00:48:15,500 --> 00:48:16,166
<c.Japanese>（泰山）</c.Japanese>
<c.Japanese>あと ひと月だけ</c.Japanese><c.Japanese>—</c.Japanese>

941
00:48:16,466 --> 00:48:17,900
<c.Japanese>援助を</c.Japanese>
<c.Japanese>続けていただけませんか</c.Japanese>

942
00:48:18,000 --> 00:48:18,833
<c.Japanese>お願いします！</c.Japanese>

943
00:48:18,933 --> 00:48:20,400
<c.Japanese>夢を叫ぶんだ！</c.Japanese>

944
00:48:20,666 --> 00:48:21,600
<c.Japanese>お父さん</c.Japanese>

945
00:48:21,700 --> 00:48:22,900
<c.Japanese>（泰山）</c.Japanese>
<c.Japanese>大きな声で叫べばな</c.Japanese><c.Japanese>—</c.Japanese>

946
00:48:23,000 --> 00:48:24,100
<c.Japanese>夢は必ずかなうんだぞ</c.Japanese>

947
00:48:24,466 --> 00:48:26,166
<c.Japanese>（翔）本当？</c.Japanese>
<c.Japanese>（泰山）うん</c.Japanese>

